    <title>PicIt!</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="title-container">
      <h1 class="title">PICIT<i class="fa-solid fa-camera"></i></h1>
      
    </div>
    <div class="usage-container">
      <p class="how-to-use">HOW TO USE:</p><br>
      <p class="how-to-use">1. Upload a picture from your local library.</p><br>
      <p class="how-to-use">2. It will show the words analized on the scree.</p><br>
      <p class="how-to-use">3. Delete the words that you alreay know.</p><br>
      <p class="how-to-use">4. Save the words for later study!</p><br>
    </div>
    <form
      action="/result"
      method="POST"
      enctype="multipart/form-data"
      class="form-container"
    >
      <input type="file" name="image" class="upload-img" />
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">업로드</button>
    </form>
    <div class="project-desc-container">
      <p class="project-desc-title">찍고, 올리고, 공부하세요!</p>
      <p class="about-project">PicIt!은 OCR과 NLP분석을 활용한 단어 공부를 도와주는 웹사이트입니다. 영어로 되어있는 문서의 단어들을 공부하고 싶을 때 그저 사진을 찍어서 이곳에 올려주세요! PicIt!은 사진안에 있는 단어들을 발견하고 보여드릴 거에요. </p>
    </div>
      <div class="footer-container">
        <marquee class="footer" behavior="scroll">
          Developed by Jiwoong Shinn, Sungwon Yuk. As a part of the graduation project @SEOULTECH.
        </marquee>
      </div>
    </div>
